tuelle Rechtsprechung eingearbeitet.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 7aLAW / Corporate.2bisacsh1 aHommelhoff, Peter, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aKleindiek, Detlef, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2z978311076700108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2023 Part 2z978311117804208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Law 2023z9783111318226oZDB-23-DGC40uhttps://doi.org/10.9785/978350438799040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783504387990423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783504387990/original  a978-3-11-076700-1  DG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2b2022  a978-3-11-117804-2  DG Plus PP Package 2023 Part 2b2023  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGCb2023  aZDB-23-DGGb2023